    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Block Ops 3D is a FPS game inspired by the biggest games in the genre. Complete missions, Gather loot, Earn cash, Race vehicles and Fight against other players across different Game modes and Maps. Get immersed in this semi Cartoon/Realistic world set in the Post-Apocalyptic era. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2348900/extras/de68230eb7e95f17f87ecb6d64c150e4.avif?t=1766170914\" width=594 height=170 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Easy to pickup and play</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2348900/extras/ce6a7f39edf2af7e730bffd3ceeb2777.poster.avif?t=1766170914\" width=594 height=170 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2348900/extras/ce6a7f39edf2af7e730bffd3ceeb2777.webm?t=1766170914\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2348900/extras/ce6a7f39edf2af7e730bffd3ceeb2777.mp4?t=1766170914\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Finely tuned player mechanics</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2348900/extras/93f3d7e2c73e1f5b0459e0059e41a7e4.poster.avif?t=1766170914\" width=594 height=170 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2348900/extras/93f3d7e2c73e1f5b0459e0059e41a7e4.webm?t=1766170914\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2348900/extras/93f3d7e2c73e1f5b0459e0059e41a7e4.mp4?t=1766170914\" type=\"